When a horizontal force [`P`] is applied to corner [`C`] of the plate, point C moves a horizontal distance of [`\delta_C=[$deltaC]`] [`mm`] and the post assumes a normal strain [`\epsilon_{BA}=[$eba]\mu`] as a result. Determine the "average" shear strain in the plate with respect to corner O.

